.IP "\(bu" 4
Add support for \*(L"## use critic (blah)\*(R".
.Sp
If I've got:
.Sp
.Vb 1
\&    ## no critic (SomePolicy)
\&
\&    ...
\&
\&    ## no critic (ADifferentPolicy)
\&
\&    ...
\&
\&    ## no critic (YetAnotherPolicy)
