.Sp
.Vb 2
\&    ## use critic
\&    ## no critic (SomePolicy, ADifferentPolicy)
.Ve
.Sp
Why can't I do this:
.Sp
.Vb 1
\&    ## use critic (SomeOtherPolicy)
.Ve
