.Sp
Require a \f(CW\*(C`=head1 NAME\*(C'\fR \s-1POD\s0 section with content that matches
\&\f(CW\*(C`\eA \es* [\ew:]+ \es+ \- \es+ \eS\*(C'\fR.  The single hyphen is the important bit.  Also,
must be a single line.
